1. Follow the connections scheme that can be found in the ReadMe file and in Assets folder
2. Upload the code to each board using Arduino IDE
3. Download Arduino libraries:
    ESP32-audioI2S-master
    Firebase Arduino Client Library for ESP8266 and ESP32
    ArduinoJson
4. Install the mobile application on your phone
5. Press the button to capture an image and receive a notification on your phone
6. View the live stream on your phone using the mobile application
